</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_134" id="67r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_134_r2l15">Den von <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_134_r2l16"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> wır <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> wıe daʒ groſſ <expan>gew<ex>er</ex>b</expan> vnd <expan>ſamnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r2l17">dem Otenwald vnd daſelbſtumb <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> ſey . Bıtten wır eẅr <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r2l18">mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſʒ daʒ Jr vns bey <expan>dıſ<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet . VVas Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r2l19">dauon <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> vnd gehört habt . <expan>vv<ex>er</ex>e</expan> aber daʒ Jr kein <expan>aıgenſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> dauon </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r2l20">
<add>weſt <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan></add> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> hett / daʒ Jr denn eẅr vorſch vnd <expan>kuntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> darauf habt Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r2l21">ob ır ıht treffenlıchs erfürt <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> gewar württ / daʒ Jr vns das allweg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r2l22"><expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıbt</expan> vnd bey eẅrſelbs <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> ſchıkt ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r2l23">bottenlon <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> becʒaln / vnd vns in den <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> guten <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> be = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r2l24">weıſet / als etc das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır vmb eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r2l25"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab facs="#facs_134_r2l26">Den von Sweinfurt
                            <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> excepto da der ſteet /
                        Otenwald . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r2l27">man da ſecʒ in der Püchen </ab>
