</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_134" id="67r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vernom<ex>en,</ex></expan> wie daz gross
                            <expan>gew<ex>er</ex>b</expan> und <expan>samnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> auf
                        dem Otenwald und daselbstumb <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> sey. Bitten
                        wir ewr <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ir uns bey
                                <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet, was ir davon
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und gehört habt.
                                <expan>W<ex>er</ex>e</expan> aber, daz ir kein
                                <expan>aigensch<ex>aft</ex></expan> davon <add>west
                                    <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan></add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> hett, daz ir denn ewr vorsch und
                                <expan>kuntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> darauf habt, und ob ir iht
                        treffenlichs erfürt <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> gewar württ, daz ir uns das
                        allweg <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibt</expan> und bey ewrselbs
                            <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> schikt, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir die bottenlon <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beczaln. Und uns in den
                                <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> guten <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> be weiset,
                        als etc. Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb ewr
                                <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        ut <expan>sup<ex>ra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Den von Sweinfurt <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> excepto da der
                        steet Otenwald, daz man da secz in der Püchen. </ab>
</div>
